OL,3,CJust how bad has Sheffield United's
OL,4,Cseason been?
OL,6,FOn Wednesday night Sheffield United
OL,7,Fclaimed the unwanted record of the
OL,8,Fmost goals conceded in a 38-game
OL,9,FPremier League season.
OL,11,FThe last of Manchester United's goals
OL,12,Fin the 4-2 defeat at Old Trafford was
OL,13,Fthe 92nd time the Blades goalkeeper
OL,14,Fhas had to pick the ball out of the
OL,15,Fnet since the season began with a
OL,16,Frelatively narrow 1-0 loss against
OL,17,FCrystal Palace.
OL,19,FSheffield United could still threaten
OL,20,Fthe record set for goals conceded in a
OL,21,F42-game season.
