OL,3,CJust how bad has Sheffield United's
OL,4,Cseason been?
OL,6,FBut just how bad has their season been?
OL,8,FThe Blades have won only three of
OL,9,Ftheir 34 league games this season and
OL,10,Fsit bottom of the table on 16 points,
OL,11,Fwith four games to go. They could be
OL,12,Frelegated as early as this weekend.
OL,14,FBack-to-back defeats conceding four
OL,15,Fgoals, with the Old Trafford game
OL,16,Fcoming on the back of a 4-1 loss to
OL,17,FBurnley, have left them on the brink.
OL,19,FBut those results are from their
OL,20,Fheaviest losses of the season.
