OL,3,CJust how bad has Sheffield United's
OL,4,Cseason been?
OL,6,FA 5-0 defeat in their reverse fixture
OL,7,Fat the Clarets was matched by the same
OL,8,Fscoreline against each of Aston Villa,
OL,9,FBrighton and Arsenal.
OL,11,FThe Gunners went one better by beating
OL,12,Fthe Blades 6-0 at Bramall Lane last
OL,13,Fmonth.
OL,15,FBut even that demoralising scoreline
OL,16,Fwas surpassed by an 8-0 defeat at the
OL,17,Fhands of Newcastle in September.
