OL,3,CJust how bad has Sheffield United's
OL,4,Cseason been?
OL,6,FAnd the Blades have already avoided
OL,7,Fthe ignominy of finishing a Premier
OL,8,FLeague season with a record low points
OL,9,Ftotal ` that distinction remains Derby
OL,10,FCounty's 11 points in 2007-08. Derby
OL,11,Fwon just one game that season.
OL,13,FBut they could still end up with a
OL,14,Fworse goal difference than the -69
OL,15,FDerby ended with that season.
OL,17,FIt is likely to be a close-run thing `
OL,18,Fthe Blades' current goal difference is
OL,19,F-59, an average of -1.73 per game. If
OL,20,Fthat trend continues they would come
OL,21,Fin just short of Derby's record at -66.
