OL,3,CJust how bad has Sheffield United's
OL,4,Cseason been?
OL,6,FBut they could become only the second
OL,7,FPremier League team to concede 100
OL,8,Ftimes in a season ` their average of
OL,9,F2.71 goals conceded per game has them
OL,10,Fon course for a record 103. Swindon
OL,11,Fconceded exactly 100 in 1993-94, when
OL,12,Fthey played four more games than
OL,13,FSheffield United will have completed
OL,14,Fby the end of this season.
OL,16,FAnd at less than half a point per
OL,17,Fgame, they need at least four from
OL,18,Ftheir remaining four games to avoid
OL,19,Fbecoming the seventh team to finish
OL,20,Fwith fewer than 20 points.
